- 2026-05-26 - Color picker UX hardening + saved colors: completed.
  - Saved colors persisted in localStorage under localtools.saved-colors.
  - Pin badge (always visible) on saved swatches → hover swaps to × to unpin.
  - - badge (hover-only) on unsaved recent swatches to pin.
