- 2026-05-26 - Slider numeric animation (CountUp): completed.
  - Added shared CountUp component using motion/react animate() tween (0.12s, custom bezier).
  - Replaces spring-based approach — no deceleration brake at end of animation.
  - ToolSlider uses CountUp for numeric displayValue; falls back to CSS num-tick for non-numeric.
  - useReducer used instead of useState in effect to satisfy react-hooks/set-state-in-effect.
  - Validation: eslint clean, tests pass.
- 2026-05-26 - UX fixes: completed.
  - Search bar padding fixed in compact mode (aside-search class exclusion).
