- 2026-05-27 - Performance pass (partial): completed.
  - Identified LCP bottleneck: avatar preview `<img>` has 5426ms render delay due to React #418 hydration error causing full CSR fallback.
  - Fixed `legal-page.tsx` hydration mismatch: `typeof window` in `useState` init → always "en" + rAF-deferred `useEffect`.
  - Fixed `qr-generator-tool.tsx`: `qrcode` static import → dynamic inside handler (~30kB removed from initial bundle).
  - Added `fetchPriority="high"` + `loading="eager"` to LCP image in `avatar-generator-tool.tsx`.
  - React #418 on main page still present — source requires dev-mode browser investigation. Render delay likely drops significantly once fixed.
  - Validation: typecheck clean, build passed.

