  - Removed hover transform from the raster asset to avoid resampling blur.
  - Served carousel WebP assets unoptimized so the original files render consistently.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Carousel final card clipping fix: completed.
  - Removed the right-side rail mask fade that clipped the last card while scrolling.
  - Added a real end buffer to the carousel track so the final card and hover scale fit before the viewport cut.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Carousel right-edge fade restored: completed.
  - Restored the right-side carousel fade using the same mask system as the left edge.
  - Keeps right fade at start/middle and disables it only at the end state so the last card remains visible.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Carousel edge fade strength increase: completed.
  - Increased carousel mask fade width so left/right edge fading is more visible.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Carousel arrow press feedback: completed.
  - Added hover scale and active press scale to the top-right carousel arrow buttons.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Carousel asset hover motion refinement: completed.
  - Enhanced carousel card asset hover with lift, zoom, and slight rotation while preserving the card scale.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Carousel image hover scale restored: completed.
  - Restored image hover/focus scale with a conservative `1.035` transform while keeping unoptimized WebP rendering.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final section vertical margin rebalance: completed.
  - Kept the final section at one viewport height while reducing card row heights.
  - Centered top and bottom card groups inside the viewport and increased vertical margins above/below them.
  - Slightly reduced final-section type/media scale so content fits inside shorter cards.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust asset scale and dots refinement: completed.
  - Increased the first final-section privacy asset size after the vertical rebalance made it too small.
  - Added more tonal dots/bubbles over the asset with stronger contrast and wider distribution.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust dots density increase: completed.
  - Rebuilt the privacy asset dot overlay with many more points.
  - Mixed dot sizes and white/gray tones for stronger layered depth.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust dots layer/theme correction: completed.
  - Moved privacy dots behind the asset instead of above it.
  - Added many more dots using mixed sizes across two CSS layers.
  - Added theme-aware dot colors: visible gray tones in light mode, gray/white tones in dark mode.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust dots proximity refinement: completed.
  - Concentrated the privacy dots closer to the lock asset so they read as a backing field instead of a square pattern.
  - Added additional nearby dots while keeping them behind the asset.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust subtitle scale: completed.
  - Increased the privacy/trust subtitle size without affecting lower card subtitles.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust body copy fit: completed.
  - Increased the two privacy body paragraphs and centered them better inside the top card.
  - Added bottom breathing room so the text no longer feels top-heavy.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust checks scale: completed.
  - Increased privacy check text size, icon size, and row gap.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust copy/checks width rebalance: completed.
  - Reduced central privacy copy width and gave more column space to the right-side check list.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Next image quality config: completed.
  - Added `images.qualities: [75, 100]` in `next.config.ts` so `next/image` accepts the carousel asset quality setting.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Overview GSAP selector cleanup: completed.
  - Restored the global class hooks GSAP expects on the hero and story sections (`subLead`, `heroText`, `heroMeta`, `heroAssetShape`, `story`).
  - Marked the first carousel asset `loading="eager"` to address the above-the-fold LCP warning.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust four-block grid: completed.
  - Split the top final card into four clear desktop blocks: asset, heading/subtitle, body paragraphs, and checks.
  - Increased the privacy asset size while preserving the one-viewport section fit.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust block vertical centering: completed.
  - Reworked the top trust card internal grid so the title/subtitle, body copy, checks, and asset sit centered in the card instead of drifting to the top.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust card true center band: completed.
  - Changed the trust card to use a centered middle band with top and bottom breathing room, so copy no longer rides the top edge.
  - Kept asset left, title/subtitle, body copy, and checks inside the card.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust card scale up inside center band: completed.
  - Increased the trust card minimum/maximum height and enlarged the subtitle, body copy, and check list so the middle band fills more of the card.
  - Increased spacing between check rows and between the body paragraphs.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final section circle shape guard: completed.
  - Explicitly disabled `corner-shape` on privacy dot/circle layers and mini indicators.
  - Added circular clipping where needed so dots stay round under the global squircle system.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust dots clipping rollback: completed.
  - Removed the `clip-path` from the privacy dot shadow layer because it clipped many of the generated dots.
  - Kept `corner-shape: unset` so dots are not affected by the global squircle rule.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Corner-shape circle trap documented/fixed: completed.
  - Changed privacy dot/indicator circle overrides from `corner-shape: unset` to `corner-shape: round !important` with `border-radius: 50% !important`.
  - Documented the global squircle/circle trap and required fix in `docs/agents/issue-tracker.md`.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Final trust card asset replacement: completed.
  - Replaced the final privacy/trust card lock asset with the provided WebP from Downloads.
  - Standardized filename to `/overview/discover-privacy-lock.webp`.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` and `bun run build` passed.
- 2026-06-03 - Footer bottom spacing: completed.
  - Increased footer bottom padding on mobile and desktop so the footer no longer sits too close to the viewport/page bottom.
  - Validation: `bun run typecheck` passed.

